  "dialog.shortcuts.title": "Keyboard Shortcuts",
  "dialog.shortcuts.content": "<h2>Keyboard Shortcuts</h2><table cellpadding='5'><tr><th align='left'>Action</th><th align='left'>Shortcut</th></tr><tr><td colspan='2'><b>File</b></td></tr><tr><td>New liturgy</td><td>Ctrl+N</td></tr><tr><td>Open liturgy</td><td>Ctrl+O</td></tr><tr><td>Save liturgy</td><td>Ctrl+S</td></tr><tr><td>Save as</td><td>Ctrl+Shift+S</td></tr><tr><td>Export</td><td>Ctrl+E</td></tr><tr><td colspan='2'><b>Edit</b></td></tr><tr><td>Delete selected</td><td>Delete</td></tr><tr><td>Move up</td><td>Ctrl+Up</td></tr><tr><td>Move down</td><td>Ctrl+Down</td></tr><tr><td colspan='2'><b>Navigation</b></td></tr><tr><td>Help</td><td>F1</td></tr></table><h3>Tips</h3><ul><li>Double-click an item to edit it</li><li>Right-click for context menu</li><li>Drag and drop to reorder items</li></ul>",

  "dialog.workflow.title": "Weekly Workflow Guide",
  "dialog.workflow.content": "<h2>Weekly Workflow Guide</h2><h3>Monday - Tuesday</h3><ul><li>Receive service order from pastor/worship leader</li><li>Open Liturgy Builder and create new liturgy (Ctrl+N)</li><li>Set service date and leader in Service Info panel</li><li>Add all elements in order: songs, readings, prayers, offerings</li><li>Save liturgy (Ctrl+S)</li></ul><h3>Wednesday</h3><ul><li>Review and verify all content</li><li>Check YouTube links (Tools &gt; Check YouTube links)</li><li>Export links overview (.txt) for musicians</li><li>Share links file with worship team</li></ul><h3>Thursday - Friday</h3><ul><li>Make any adjustments based on feedback</li><li>Fill in any remaining fields (Edit all fields)</li><li>Verify all slides have content (no stubs)</li></ul><h3>Saturday</h3><ul><li>Final review of liturgy</li><li>Export PowerPoint (.pptx)</li><li>Export PDF bundle for musicians if needed</li><li>Update Excel register if configured</li><li>Test presentation on church computer</li></ul><h3>Sunday</h3><ul><li>Open exported PowerPoint</li><li>Run presentation during service</li></ul><h3>Best Practices</h3><ul><li>Keep song library organized by category</li><li>Update YouTube links when videos become unavailable</li><li>Use theme templates for consistent service structure</li><li>Train backup operators on the software</li><li>Back up liturgy files regularly</li></ul>",

